---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Akash Mahajan</p>

    <h1 class="hero-title reveal reveal-d1">
      I've spent 24 years learning<br />
      <span class="hero-accent">what breaks in production.</span>
    </h1>

    <p class="hero-desc reveal reveal-d2">
      Now I build the security tools and infrastructure that keep
      AI agents, LLM-powered products, and cloud systems safe.
      Two companies. 26 active projects. Everything I learn, I share.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-companies reveal reveal-d2">
      <a href="https://kloudle.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hero-company">
        <span class="hc-name">Kloudle</span>
        <span class="hc-desc">Cloud security scanning for teams shipping with AI agents</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://appsecco.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="hero-company">
        <span class="hc-name">Appsecco</span>
        <span class="hc-desc">Product security testing for apps, APIs, and AI integrations</span>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-follow reveal reveal-d3">
      <a href="https://x.com/makash" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="follow-btn follow-primary">Follow on X</a>
      <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/akashm/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="follow-btn">LinkedIn</a>
      <a href="https://github.com/makash" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="follow-btn">GitHub</a>
      <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@makash" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="follow-btn">YouTube</a>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-proof reveal reveal-d3">
      <div class="proof-items">
        <span class="proof-item">Author of 2 books by Packt</span>
        <span class="proof-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="proof-item">Recommended by PortSwigger</span>
        <span class="proof-sep">&middot;</span>
        <span class="proof-item">Co-founded null — India's open security community</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 90vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 10rem var(--gutter) 6rem;
  }

  .hero-inner {
    max-width: var(--max-w);
    margin: 0 auto;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.25rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .hero-accent { color: var(--color-accent); }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    max-width: 36rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.85;
  }

  .hero-companies {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--color-border);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    max-width: 38rem;
  }

  .hero-company {
    flex: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.3rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-text);
    transition: background 0.15s;
  }
  .hero-company:hover { background: var(--color-surface-hover); color: var(--color-text); }

  .hc-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display), Georgia, serif;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }

  .hc-desc {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .hero-follow {
    display: flex;
    gap: 0.6rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .follow-btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0.65rem 1.25rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-light);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    font-family: var(--font-sans), system-ui, sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    transition: all 0.15s ease;
  }
  .follow-btn:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .follow-primary {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: #fff;
  }
  .follow-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
    border-color: var(--color-accent-hover);
    color: #fff;
  }

  .hero-proof { max-width: 38rem; }

  .proof-items {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
  }

  .proof-sep { opacity: 0.3; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .hero { min-height: auto; padding: 8rem var(--gutter) 4rem; }
    .hero-companies { flex-direction: column; }
    .follow-btn { padding: 0.6rem 1rem; font-size: 0.8rem; }
  }
</style>
